{
  "stem": "27767.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were some other people around there, gentile people, Hungarians, because it was a-- there were-- this town was mostly Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Romanian-- there lived some Romanian peoples too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the Romanians mostly around the-- around the town in small-- and other religious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But most of the townspeople were Hungarians, actually.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we had with the population-- we had very good relationships in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And potentially started when-- in 19-- it was still Romania in 1938 when the-- when the Guardists came, the-- the Iron Guard came to power in Romania.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a lot-- a lot of antisemitism therein.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember, in 1938, they-- as soon as they came to power, they gave-- they gave out a decree.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have to open the store in Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that was a very big thing because my parents were religious.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so they had to open.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and it was only one week because that government fall after two weeks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the King Carol-- Carol was the king of Romania at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He took over the government at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so they fell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was a lot of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember my teachers was a family-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was their name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was also the-- from-- connected with Iron Guard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But he was nicer to us because we grew up there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They grew up there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I remember he went to rallies, to Cluj and other parts, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and they-- and at rallies, they incited the people and against the Jews, and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I had non-Jewish friends in the school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were very good friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were good friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember I had a very good friend.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
